instructions: Tap More, then tap Purchased. If you set up Family Sharing, choose a family member to view their purchases. Note: You can see purchases made by family members only if they choose to share their purchases. Tap Music, Movies, or TV Shows. Find the item you want to download, then tap the Download button .

Go to Settings > iTunes & App Store, then tap your Apple ID. Tap View Apple ID. In Account Settings, tap Subscriptions, then tap a subscribed service. Choose a different subscription option or tap Cancel Subscription.
